            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "If you type after the inline virtual text in Terminal mode, you'll see that the cursor position is also off:\n```lua\nlocal api = vim.api\nvim.cmd.terminal([[printf \"\\033[32mGREEN\\033[0m>\"; cat]])\nvim.defer_fn(function()\n  local ns = api.nvim_create_namespace('highlight')\n  api.nvim_buf_set_extmark(0, ns, 0, 0, {\n    virt_text_pos = 'inline',\n    virt_text = { { 'abc', 'Error' } },\n  })\nend, 100)\nvim.cmd.startinsert()\n```\n\n<img width=\"225\" height=\"143\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/088bc99c-e161-4759-b699-65743a39580f\" />",
